    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Model elements</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;">Model element commands</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">There are two commands in the <text styleclass="T_Menu">Mechanism menu</text> that you can use in the <text styleclass="Interface2">Model-Editor</text> and in <text styleclass="Interface2">Mechanism-Editors</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text">Use the two commands to arrange the basic layout of your machine.</text></para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Mechanism</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> - to add a new </text><text styleclass="Interface2">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> working environment, with a </text><text styleclass="Element-Header">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> as the reference element.</text></li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> - to add a </text><text styleclass="Element-Header">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> that is offset from a different </text><text styleclass="Element-Header">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Interface2" style="color:#ff0000;">Important</text>: </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You <text styleclass="Interface2" style="color:#ff0000;">must</text> use the <text styleclass="Interface2">Model-Editor</text> to add a minimum of one <text styleclass="Interface2">Mechanism-Editor</text> to a <text styleclass="Element-Header">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Modelelements(Model)-AddMechanism" styleclass="SeeAlso">Model elements &gt; Add Mechanism</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><conditional-text type="IF" value="PROFESSIONAL"/>MD16 : Add menu&gt; Model elements</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">There are two commands to add <text styleclass="VariableName">Model elements</text> in the <text styleclass="T_Menu">Add menu</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="MD-Menu-Bar-Add-Modelmenu.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><title>Add menu &gt; Model elements (MD16)</title><caption><![CDATA[Add menu > Model elements (MD16)]]></caption></image><conditional-text type="ELSE"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Mechanism menu &gt; Model elements</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The two commands are in the <text styleclass="T_Menu">Mechanism menu</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="MD-17-Menu-Mechanism-Model.ipp" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><title>Mechanism menu &gt; Model elements (MD17)</title><caption><![CDATA[Mechanism menu > Model elements (MD17)]]></caption></image><conditional-text type="END"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><anchor id="Modeltoolbar"><keywords><keyword>Model elements toolbar</keyword></keywords></anchor>Model elements toolbar</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="T_Menu">Model elements toolbar</text> is to <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">left</text> of the graphics-area.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="MD-Toolbar-Model-A.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-weight:normal;" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Model elements toolbar]]></caption><imagemap><area shape="rect" coords="0,49,230,89" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddMechanism(Mechanism)"><title>ModelAddMech</title></area><area shape="rect" coords="0,92,230,132" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-ModelElements(Mechanism)-AddPlane"/></imagemap></image></para>
